<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="yes-adv">yes <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /jes/    美 /jes/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[对肯定的问句的回答] 是；是的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Will you come? 
你要来吗?</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Yes, I will. 
对，我要来。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[对否定的问句的回答] 不：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— You weren’t invited, were you? 
没有邀请您，是吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Yes, I was. 
不，邀请了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[同意对方的话或对自己的话加以肯定] 对；是的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Your work is good, yes, very good. 
你的工作干得很好，对，干得很好。</p></div></div>